data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS! This is a must see 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, brick & cedar home nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac, offering space to accommodate a large growing family. Before entering the heated 2 car attached garage with an additional storage room, take note of the double wide concrete driveway with a side slab for an RV or boat parking. Step into this home's foyer that offers a half bath, coat closet, and an updated mudroom. Pergo laminate wood flooring throughout Main level. Freshly painted large living room and formal dining room. Beyond the foyer you will find a family room with a gas fireplace, hardwood parquet flooring, 2 built-in shelves, and a set of French doors that opens up to the large carpeted 3 season room/enclosed patio surrounded by walls of patio doors to view the large deck and wooded backyard that host 2 large sheds. On the 2nd level you will be pleasantly pleased with the oversized master bedroom with two walk-in closets and a master bathroom. The 2nd floor is completed with 3 additional large bedrooms with ample closet space and another full bathroom. Entertain family and friends in the large finished basement that offers 2 additional rooms, one with laundry hook up. Newer electrical panel (2018). roof (2004), appliance stays (stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, garage disposal). Excellent location for dining, shopping, and close to the turnpike and major highways. Do not miss your opportunity to own this amazing property and be "home" for the holidays!!!
